  <name>Shuffleboard</name>
  <summary>A modern dashboard for FRC</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Shuffleboard is a dashboard for the FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC). 
      It communicates with the robot using NetworkTables to display robot status 
      and control settings in real-time.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time data visualization using JavaFX</li>
      <li>Record and playback of robot data</li>
      <li>Customizable layouts and themes</li>
      <li>Plugin support for custom widgets</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
